@startuml
!theme plain

title Performance Evaluation Dashboard - Component Diagram

actor User

package "Web Layer (Browser)" {
  [Dashboard UI]
  [Modal Forms]
  [Profile Display]
}

package "Backend Layer (FastAPI)" {
  [FastAPI App]
  [AI Generator]
  [Conversation Engine]
}

package "Data Layer" {
  database "SQLite Database" as DB
  [JSON Storage]
}

package "External Services" {
  [LLM Service]
}

' --- Relationships ---

' User Interaction
User --> [Dashboard UI] : Interacts with

' Web Layer Composition
[Dashboard UI] -- [Modal Forms] : contains
[Dashboard UI] -- [Profile Display] : contains

' Web Layer to Backend Layer
[Dashboard UI] --> [FastAPI App] : "HTTP API Calls\n(/api/employees, /api/project-managers, /api/conversation)"

' Backend Internal Logic
[FastAPI App] --> [AI Generator] : Uses for data generation
[FastAPI App] --> [Conversation Engine] : Manages evaluation discussions

' Backend to Data Layer
[FastAPI App] --> DB : Reads/Writes (Employees & Managers)
[Conversation Engine] --> [JSON Storage] : Reads/Writes (Conversation History)

' Backend to External Services
[AI Generator] ..> [LLM Service] : API Calls (Google/OpenAI/etc.)
[Conversation Engine] ..> [LLM Service] : API Calls for chat responses

@enduml